      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Tricky race to kick off the card with a few of these babies facing the starter for the first time. Of the raced brigade SNIPER BOOM (1) is unlucky to still be a maiden placing in both starts to date and strikes a winnable contest here. Gets some weight relief with the 2kg claim and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. SUMMER SENSATION (8) was well in the betting on debut but just missed the frame on that occasion. Where there's smoke there's fire and should be going very close. WRITTEN ACLAIM (2) performed above expectations when at the races for the first time and will have derived some experience from that hit-out. In the mix. BRAVE ETOILE (4) is on debut but has shown ability at the trials and any market confidence must be noted. THE AUTUMN AFFAIR (9) next in line from the favourable draw.",
